OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The West risks entering a nuclear war  
OL,6, because it is not talking enough to    
OL,7, Russia and China, the UK's national    
OL,8, security adviser has said.             
OL,10,FSir Stephen Lovegrove said rival powers
OL,11,Funderstood each other better during the
OL,12,FCold War, and that a lack of dialogue  
OL,13,Ftoday made miscalculations more likely.
OL,15,F"In the obligatory Churchill quotation,
OL,16,Fwe want jaw-jaw, not war-war," he said.
OL,18,FHe added that we were in a "new age of 
OL,19,Fproliferation" in which dangerous      
OL,20,Fweapons were more widely available.    
